if they see their parents drinking,

38:38.610 --> 38:40.362
they're twice as likely
to do it themselves.

38:43.990 --> 38:44.991
Yeah.

38:45.075 --> 38:46.951
I'll let myself out. Thanks.

38:49.245 --> 38:51.331
- Bye.
- Bye.

38:55.919 --> 38:58.672
<i>...control of
insurgent strongholds in the area.</i>

38:58.838 --> 39:00.006
Hello.

39:00.757 --> 39:01.800
Hiya.

39:03.301 --> 39:04.719
Is toast all right?

39:05.553 --> 39:08.890
