<i>I will be waiting...</i>

47:47.492 --> 47:50.245
All seems first-rate.
Same time next month, then.

47:50.328 --> 47:53.331
Let me just show you what the women
have been up to since your last visit.

47:55.458 --> 47:57.585
<i>...too far ahead</i>

