<i>You're calling to me</i>

48:00.714 --> 48:03.800
<i>I can't hear what you have said</i>

48:03.883 --> 48:07.053
HQ are going to love this. Fits in
perfectly with the new directives.

48:07.137 --> 48:09.848
You should have heard them
on the hike, sir. We were in...

48:09.931 --> 48:11.474
Thank you, Captain.
