<i>Time after time</i>

49:05.195 --> 49:06.571
I need to speak to you all.

49:06.654 --> 49:10.075
Oh, Jesus. Is it about the blow-up
doll we sent out to Bastion?

49:13.578 --> 49:14.579
She's joking.

49:16.039 --> 49:19.334
Brigadier Groves heard you rehearsing
when he was here a few weeks ago.

49:19.918 --> 49:21.252
