at the Festival of Remembrance.

49:30.845 --> 49:31.930
What?

49:33.431 --> 49:35.016
The Festival of
Remembrance on TV?

49:36.768 --> 49:38.228
- The big one?
- That one.

49:38.311 --> 49:39.521
At the Royal Albert Hall?

49:48.154 --> 49:49.739
I can't wait to tell my mum.

49:50.156 --> 49:52.117
Do you reckon the lads will be able
to see it out in Afghan?

49:52.200 --> 49:54.536
- Hope not.
- You don't need to worry.

49:54.619 --> 49:56.746
We are gonna be match fit
after that market gig.

49:56.830 --> 49:59.457
It's all right for you, Maz.
You haven't got to do a solo.

49:59.582 --> 50:02.210
Just see the market
as a dress rehearsal.

50:02.293 --> 50:05.171
And I'll be by your side.
Like shoulder buddies.

50:05.255 --> 50:07.841
Eh? Come on, cheer up.

50:07.924 --> 50:09.384
