Come on.

51:52.779 --> 51:55.407
<i>Time after time</i>

52:09.921 --> 52:12.549
<i>Time after time</i>

52:13.466 --> 52:14.467
<i>Time after time</i>

52:14.551 --> 52:16.094
We'll be laughed out
of the Albert Hall.

52:18.847 --> 52:20.098
I don't want to sing any more.

52:21.057 --> 52:22.642
I'm not a minor, I'm just shit!

52:22.934 --> 52:25.270
Maybe you could silently
mouth the words.

52:25.854 --> 52:26.938
Like Dawn.

52:31.526 --> 52:32.736
Erm... Marilyn?

52:33.153 --> 52:36.740
What does your football coach
say to you after a defeat?

52:37.198 --> 52:39.200
Easy. It's all about control.

52:39.284 --> 52:40.285
Exactly.

52:40.785 --> 52:42.579
A defence-splitting pass,
bring it down,

52:42.662 --> 52:43.997
knock it to the forwards. Boom.

52:46.958 --> 52:49.377
- Look, do you like singing?
- Of course we do.

52:49.461 --> 52:51.671
- Do you like being in the choir?
- Love it.

52:51.755 --> 52:54.924
Think the top brass would've asked
you to sing if you were shit?

52:55.675 --> 52:57.093
No, we just chose the wrong venue.

52:57.177 --> 52:59.137
- Yeah, and that was our fault.
- Exactly.

52:59.220 --> 53:02.474
Do you want to give up because of
that or work harder

53:02.557 --> 53:03.725
so we really kill it
at the Albert Hall?

53:03.808 --> 53:05.226
- Kill it.
- Which?

53:05.852 --> 53:07.020
- Kill it.
- Right.

53:08.605 --> 53:09.981
So how shall we do that, Kate?

53:11.524 --> 53:14.235
Er... well, we choose
a small repertoire.

53:14.319 --> 53:17.447
We practise together and at home.

53:18.156 --> 53:20.116
We tweak, we review, tweak, review

53:20.200 --> 53:22.243
until we come together
like a shoal of fish.

53:23.953 --> 53:26.456
The best Military Wives choir
in England.

53:26.790 --> 53:30.210
Well, the only Military Wives choir
in England.

53:32.504 --> 53:34.130
<i>Come on, girls.</i>

53:34.214 --> 53:36.216
<i>We're singing for England</i>

53:36.299 --> 53:37.801
<i>Eng-ger-land</i>

53:37.884 --> 53:40.011
<i>We're singing in a foreign...</i>

53:40.095 --> 53:42.263
Oi! If I'd done that...

53:42.555 --> 53:43.973
<i>For England</i>

53:44.057 --> 53:47.769
<i>You've got to hold and give
and do it at the right time</i>

53:47.852 --> 53:51.690
<i>You can be slow or fast
but you must get to the line</i>

53:53.650 --> 53:55.318
Behold our choir.

53:55.860 --> 53:57.862
Dignified, noble.

53:58.530 --> 53:59.531
Class.

53:59.614 --> 54:02.992
<i>So catch me if you can
cos I'm an England woman</i>

54:04.160 --> 54:05.829
What would your karaoke song be?

54:06.246 --> 54:08.206
Karaoke's my idea of hell.

54:08.289 --> 54:10.166
But if you had to,
if you'd no choice?

54:11.418 --> 54:14.337
Well,
I did do <i>Tainted Love</i> once.

54:14.421 --> 54:16.381
